<i>noun</i>: 훼방 [훼ː방], 비방 [비방] <i>verb</i>: 훼방하다 [훼ː방하다] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>훼방 [훼ː방]</dt><br>
<dd>1. slander; libel</dd><br>
<dd>남을 해치려고 나쁘게 말함.</dd><br>
<dd>An act of speaking ill of another to do harm to him/her.</dd><br>
<dd>2. interruption; disturbance; obstruction</dd><br>
<dd>남의 일을 방해함.</dd><br>
<dd>An act of interrupting another's affair.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>비방 [비방]</dt><br>
<dd>slander; libel</dd><br>
<dd>남을 깎아내리거나 해치는 말을 함. 또는 그런 말.</dd><br>
<dd>An act of degrading or speaking ill of others; or such a remark.</dd><br>
</li>
<li><i>verb</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>훼방하다 [훼ː방하다]</dt><br>
<dd>1. slander; libel</dd><br>
<dd>남을 해치려고 나쁘게 말하다.</dd><br>
<dd>To speak ill of another to do harm to him/her.</dd><br>
<dd>2. interrupt; disturb; obstruct</dd><br>
<dd>남의 일을 방해하다.</dd><br>
<dd>To interrupt another's affair.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>